xlink|Potato yellow mosaic virus|species}}|{{taxlink|Potato yellow vein virus|species}}\n| potayto, potahto|potomato|{{vern|prairie potato}} ({{taxlink|Psoralea esculenta|species}})|prepotato|[[Price's potato-bean]] ({{taxlink|Apios priceana|species}})|{{vern|prickly potato}} ({{taxlink|Solanum triflorum|species}})|purple Peruvian potato|purple potato\n| red potato|red round potato|red-skinned potato|russet potato|Russian blue potato\n| salt potatoes|sautéed potato|scalloped potatoes|[[sea potato]] ({{taxlink|Echinocardium cordatum|species}})|{{vern|seaside potato}} ({{taxlink|Ipomoea pes-caprae|species}})|seed potato|see you later, baked potato|shoestring potatoes|small potatoes|small potatoes and a few in a hill,small potatoes and a few in the hill|smashed potato,smashed potatoes|Spanish potato|starchy potato|{{vern|swamp potato}} ({{taxfmt|Sagittaria|genus}} spp.)|sweet potato\n| tater|Telinga potatomtelingo potato|{{vern|ten-lined potato beetle}} ({{taxfmt|Leptinotarsa decemlineata|species}})|tomtato|tornado potato|tropical sweet potato\n| Vivaldi potato|volcano potato\n| waxy potato|white-fleshed sweet potato|white potato|{{vern|white potato vine}}|{{taxlink|Wild potato mosaic virus|species}}|white round potato|white sweet potato|[[wild potato]] ({{taxlink|Peltandra virginica|species}})|wild potato vine\n| yellow dwarf of potato|yellow potato\n| Zulu potato,Zulu round potato\n}}\n\n====Translations====\n{{trans-top|plant tuber eaten as starchy vegetable}}\n* Abkhaz: {{t|ab|акартош}}\n* Afrikaans: {{t+|af|aartappel}}, {{t+|af|ertappel}}\n* Albanian: {{t+|sq|patate}}, {{t+|sq|kërtollë}}\n* Ambonese Malay: {{t|abs|artapel}}\n* Amharic: {{t|am|ድንች}}\n* Arabic: {{t+|ar|بَطَاطَا|f}}, {{t+|ar|بَطَاطِس|m}}\n*: Egyptian Arabic: {{t|arz|بطاطس|m|tr=baṭāṭes}} {{qualifier|collective}}, {{t|arz|بطاطساية|f|tr=baṭaṭsāya}} (''[[singulative]]'')\n*: Gulf Arabic: {{t|afb|آلو|tr=ālo}}, {{t|afb|بُطاط|tr=buṭāṭ}}\n*: Hijazi Arabic: {{t|acw|بَطَاطِس|m|tr=baṭāṭis}}\n*: Moroccan Arabic: